<h2 id="freedom-of-information-foi">Freedom of information (<abbr title="freedom of information">FOI</abbr>)</h2>

<p>We recommend that you don’t use our social media channels for making <abbr title="freedom of information">FOI</abbr> requests.</p>

<p>To make an <abbr title="freedom of information">FOI</abbr> request, please contact us directly.</p>

